表格注塑机管理的代码预览

if exists (select 1
from sysobjects
where id = object_id('MachineMstr')
and type = 'U')
drop table MachineMstr
go

/*==============================================================*/
/* Table: MachineMstr */
/*==============================================================*/
create table MachineMstr (
ID int identity(1,1),
Machine_Code varchar(50) not null,
Machine_Type varchar(50) null,
Machine_Manufacturer varchar(50) null,
Machine_AssetNo varchar(20) null,
Machine_EquipmentNo varchar(50) null,
Machine_MadeDate datetime null,
Machine_PurchaseDate datetime null,
Machine_LockPower integer null constraint DF_MachineMstr_JH_Machine_LockPower default (0),
Machine_ShotQty decimal(18, 0) null constraint DF_MachineMstr_JH_Machine_ShotQty default (0),
Machine_PushDistance decimal(18, 0) null constraint DF_MachineMstr_JH_Machine_PushDistance default (0),
Machine_LoadMouldLgt decimal(18, 0) null constraint DF_MachineMstr_JH_Machine_LoadMouldLgt default (0),
Machine_LoadMouldWdt decimal(18, 0) null constraint DF_MachineMstr_JH_Machine_LoadMouldWdt default (0),
MinMouldThick decimal(18, 0) null constraint DF_MachineMstr_JH_MinMouldThick default (0),
MaxMouldThick decimal(18, 0) null constraint DF_MachineMstr_JH_MaxMouldThick default (0),
ShotDiameter decimal(18, 0) null constraint DF_MachineMstr_JH_ShotDiameter default (0),
HydPressTackOut char(2) null,
DrawPoleDistance decimal(18, 0) null constraint DF_MachineMstr_JH_DrawPoleDistance default (0),
Robort varchar(20) null,
Machine_Power decimal(10, 2) null constraint DF_MachineMstr_JH_Machine_Power default (0),
Machine_MaterialChgAmt decimal(18, 0) null constraint DF_MachineMstr_JH_Machine_MaterialChgAmt default (0),
Machine_Photo image null,
DispatchCount int not null constraint DF_MachineMstr_DispatchCount default 0,
Remark varchar(400) null,
constraint PK_MACHINEMSTR primary key (Machine_Code)
)
ON [PRIMARY] TEXTIMAGE_ON [PRIMARY]
END
go
